  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Appliance
    Appliances represent devices that have sensors and can be controlled.
    CommandImporter
    CommandImporter is used to execute string commands against the HouseModelService.
    EnumOptions
    EnumOptions is a behavior for the StatusOptions.
    House
    House class can contain rooms and occupants.
    HouseMateModelServiceAPI
    HouseMateModelService is the public facing API for the model service.
    HouseMateNode
    HouseMateNode extends node so that it can be used in the knowledge graph.
    Occupant
    Occupants can belong to multiple houses.
    RangeOptions
    RangeOptions is a behavior for the StatusOptions.
    Room
    A room has a floor and contains sensors and appliances.
    Sensor
    Sensors represent items like cameras and smoke detectors.
    Status
    Status follows the Strategy pattern for the option behaviors.
